<p><strong>Cribbio is a relevant example of Rexite’s research of excellence in design, using the most suitable materials for a project</strong>. Cribbio makes it even clearer that we can’t simply define these items as a mere wastebasket or an umbrella stand: they’re much more. There is a story behind them, a story that is waiting for someone to listen to it.</p>

